2010-12-28  Peter Bloomfield

	Initial commit for gtk3 development branch

	* configure.in:
	* libbalsa/address-view.c (lbav_key_pressed_cb):
	* libbalsa/body.c (libbalsa_message_body_get_pixbuf):
